I"C<h2 id="create">Create</h2>

<p><strong>STEP-1</strong>: Click on <strong>New -&gt; Attendance Type Master</strong>. Attendance Type Master form will appear.</p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_54.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p><strong>STEP-2</strong>: Fill the details and click on <strong>Save</strong>.</p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_55.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<h2 id="list">List</h2>

<p>Click on <strong>Master -&gt; Attendance Type Master</strong>. Attendance Type menu will appear.</p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_56.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<h2 id="edit">Edit</h2>

<p><strong>STEP-1</strong>: Select attendance type from the list and right click on it. Select <strong>Edit Attendance Tag Master option</strong>.</p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_57.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p><strong>STEP-2</strong>: Edit the details and click on <strong>Save</strong>.</p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_58.jpg" alt="" /></p>
